Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.25,0:00:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小晶 起床了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.59,0:00:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好~~~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.21,0:00:15.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.15,0:00:17.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯~~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.94,0:00:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬季的校服給你掛在那了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.16,0:00:24.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬季的校服？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.47,0:00:32.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 到換季的時候了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.88,0:01:58.83,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs46}{\pos(352,275)}冬 日 花 火
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.35,0:02:08.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然因睡回籠覺搞得遲到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.83,0:02:11.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是小學生啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.09,0:02:16.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正順路 要我送你到學校嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.71,0:02:18.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送到車站前就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.76,0:02:22.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富美醬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.74,0:02:25.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.96,0:02:30.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡迷糊了 讓哥哥開車送我來的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.14,0:02:33.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就猜想會不會是這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.54,0:02:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一片秋天已經到來的感覺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.60,0:02:48.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.52,0:02:59.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年的夏天 真短呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.92,0:03:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺一下子就過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.23,0:03:04.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.31,0:03:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,替換書嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.52,0:03:38.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 要把圖書館裏的舊書處理掉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.18,0:03:43.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光靠圖書委員忙不過來 所以一直都借我們過去幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.31,0:03:47.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在書架上找到的話 就放到箱子裏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.37,0:03:49.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬城目同學就有勞負責世界文學的那塊了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.25,0:03:52.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果列表上的書被借出去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.82,0:03:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種情況的書在列表前標有星號的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.43,0:03:57.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用找也行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.49,0:04:12.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,《廣闊的藻海》…《廣闊的藻海》…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.02,0:04:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.98,0:04:25.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,《達洛衛夫人》…《達洛衛夫人》…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.24,0:04:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…心理準備
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.84,0:04:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.91,0:04:50.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬城目同學 別停下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.26,0:04:51.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.96,0:04:52.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.98,0:04:56.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以停下來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.73,0:04:59.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧 上當了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.48,0:05:00.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小本 模仿的漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.24,0:05:02.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好過分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.62,0:05:04.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到萬城目同學啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.51,0:05:06.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就想作弄一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.65,0:05:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.95,0:05:10.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別太打擾我們幹活哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.48,0:05:11.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.30,0:05:16.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這活被稱為是文藝部的稅金哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.60,0:05:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稅金？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.88,0:05:21.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 文藝部不是經常到圖書館借書嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.09,0:05:26.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以作為交換要幫圖書館幹活
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.21,0:05:31.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們戲劇部借的書很少 所以沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.02,0:05:33.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}高中生戲劇2003賞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.31,0:05:37.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一回戲劇祭的表演節目從這裏面選
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.31,0:05:37.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}《我的小鎮》《雲雀》《鹿鳴館》
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.14,0:05:42.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明年要投票決定 所以今年你們要全部讀完
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.70,0:05:45.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年生明年也要登台演出
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.11,0:05:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要設身處地 用心去讀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.60,0:05:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.83,0:05:55.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就要畢業了 貌似和我們沒什麼關係呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.75,0:05:56.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.76,0:05:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種不付責任的發言無視就好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.17,0:06:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,構圖我想已經畫的很不錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.22,0:06:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後就是為了突顯物的存在感 大膽的去畫一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.57,0:06:13.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.54,0:06:16.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和佐 能接下電話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.41,0:06:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方說的是英文 我聽不太懂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.01,0:06:21.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是恭己的留學的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.07,0:06:23.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是沒辦法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.88,0:06:28.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.63,0:06:32.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杉本學姐要去國外嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.06,0:06:35.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我想遲早會公開的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.58,0:06:37.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但現在能暫時幫忙保密嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.39,0:06:41.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙不太喜歡別人知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.10,0:07:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富美醬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.68,0:07:55.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到剛才為止我都是以為自己已經徹底了斷的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.59,0:07:56.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.46,0:08:02.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不怪你啊 轉換心情又不像按個開關那麼簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.22,0:08:10.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己感覺連自己都無法搞懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.91,0:08:14.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富美醬 我們吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.24,0:08:17.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候吃就是最好的療法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.08,0:08:19.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要栗子蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.68,0:08:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我要蘋果派
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.63,0:08:26.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服務員~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.91,0:08:59.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杉本學姐真的是全能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.49,0:09:01.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好景仰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.47,0:09:05.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個杉本學姐要去留學的傳言 你聽說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.17,0:09:08.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到了 說是要去倫敦的大學…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.41,0:09:09.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧？真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.24,0:09:12.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣 深受打擊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.13,0:09:18.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說你要去英國留學了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.36,0:09:23.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送上平凡一句  留學，請加油
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.07,0:09:27.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果當面說的話 說不定會當場哭起來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.47,0:09:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以用郵件代替了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.80,0:09:33.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和佐老師的畫畫課我打算繼續學下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.52,0:09:34.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,京子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.11,0:09:50.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖誕夜？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.74,0:09:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.15,0:09:53.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是有空…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.05,0:09:54.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有空…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.02,0:09:55.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.16,0:10:01.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小晶呢 跟我說「要不要叫上大家開個聖誕晚會」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.37,0:10:02.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.77,0:10:04.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話 也來進行禮物交換吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.94,0:10:06.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 贊成
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.33,0:10:10.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家反響非常強烈 都很期待
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.26,0:10:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 如果井汲同學再能來就最好不過了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.74,0:10:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,井汲同學不來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.60,0:10:20.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像和澤乃井先生約好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.60,0:10:23.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 有點遺憾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.84,0:10:28.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.10,0:10:31.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富美 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.18,0:10:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個 千津姐送來的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.19,0:10:47.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們搬家了 富美醬抽時間來玩哦 --千津姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.22,0:10:54.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 富美 還記得自己的初戀嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.63,0:10:59.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一個喜歡上的人 富美還記得嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.06,0:11:05.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一個喜歡上的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.06,0:11:16.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 這裏是奧平家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.93,0:11:18.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 我是澤乃井
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.00,0:11:19.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,康先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.24,0:11:23.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我有事想拜託你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.57,0:11:29.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然叫你出來 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.10,0:11:31.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為沒其他人可以拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.42,0:11:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 我也正好要買東西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.96,0:11:37.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過稍微有點顧慮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.42,0:11:42.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 以奧平你的興趣選的東西絕對沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.25,0:11:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.40,0:11:47.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我選的東西總是被她一下就猜到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.19,0:11:51.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然沒什麼自信 但我試試看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.92,0:12:09.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.71,0:12:10.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.65,0:12:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不行嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.25,0:12:19.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我覺得可以
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.06,0:12:21.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 就這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.31,0:12:36.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託奧平真是對了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.34,0:12:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.56,0:12:41.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我的話絕對不會選這個的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.25,0:12:44.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是不好的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.67,0:12:47.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想她一定會中意的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.23,0:12:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.00,0:12:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.62,0:12:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.03,0:12:59.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.84,0:13:05.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的在這裏下就行了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.70,0:13:06.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.33,0:13:09.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起在這附近有點事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.32,0:13:10.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.74,0:13:14.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這次的謝禮下次遇上的時候再付吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.04,0:13:16.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去的時候小心一點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.97,0:13:17.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.64,0:13:34.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明年開始拆遷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.30,0:13:48.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不認為康先生和小晶在交往
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.00,0:13:52.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但就算在交往也沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.65,0:13:57.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是真的話  我想也會跟我說的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.55,0:14:07.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  為什麼躲起來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.40,0:14:15.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖誕快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.09,0:14:18.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經3次了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.07,0:14:19.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多做幾次又沒什麼關係嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.13,0:14:21.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋糕再來一個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.02,0:14:23.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要3份行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.00,0:14:25.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吃的下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.48,0:14:27.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  沒關係的沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.29,0:14:31.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.55,0:14:34.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  今天可能會有點吵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.55,0:14:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二到三個小時就會結束的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.74,0:14:38.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很開心嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.48,0:14:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很開心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.24,0:14:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人寂寞的過著的人那真是可憐啊可憐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.78,0:14:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可憐的我沒有禮物嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.69,0:14:48.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.86,0:14:50.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真冷淡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.67,0:14:54.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你瞧  「沒有禮物嗎」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.55,0:14:57.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放著寂寞的人不管行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.90,0:15:00.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裏 不要往奇怪的方向煽風點火
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.55,0:15:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不啊  很有趣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.21,0:15:04.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有幾個人啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.12,0:15:07.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加上晶全部有5人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.46,0:15:13.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俗話說三個女人一台戲 五個女人連續劇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.88,0:15:15.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的真過分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.92,0:15:18.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 我不在你考慮之列嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.96,0:15:22.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 你是…那個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.84,0:15:23.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.00,0:15:26.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是小晶？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.34,0:15:27.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.21,0:15:30.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿裙子的樣子真是萌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.96,0:15:36.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小晶好小啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.29,0:15:38.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小的是富美哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.17,0:15:39.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是這邊的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.00,0:15:48.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女大十八變呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.37,0:15:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有入學時的照片  看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.66,0:15:51.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要看要看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.18,0:15:54.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪個哪個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.33,0:15:58.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.06,0:16:01.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀~~沒有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.98,0:16:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校舍是木造的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.95,0:16:13.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  但是明年就要拆了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.67,0:16:16.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說要蓋新的校舍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.92,0:16:22.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.88,0:16:24.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.56,0:16:27.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會有點土氣？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.76,0:16:28.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有這事的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.08,0:16:31.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也已經是大人了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.93,0:16:33.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.64,0:16:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  阿康
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.93,0:16:47.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有件事想問一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.48,0:16:52.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的圍巾哪裏去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.93,0:16:54.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桌子的下面呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.31,0:16:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看過了 沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.13,0:16:58.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 說了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.75,0:16:59.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.23,0:17:03.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是個不錯的禮物 所以就拷問了阿康
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.68,0:17:05.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他坦白真相了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.24,0:17:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  聖誕快樂  還有新年快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.23,0:17:13.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坦白真相？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.26,0:17:14.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.48,0:17:15.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.96,0:17:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.45,0:17:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 小安的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.25,0:17:25.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  這樣的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.96,0:17:27.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？有什麼好笑的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.02,0:17:30.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了  謝謝款待
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.04,0:17:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安  路上小心點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.50,0:17:35.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.19,0:17:42.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.88,0:17:51.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.24,0:17:54.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  別看了別看了 快走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.54,0:17:59.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚 好寒好寒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.30,0:18:01.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑子 幫我打個領帶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.43,0:18:02.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.47,0:18:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬天了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.83,0:18:07.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到在那裏告白了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.06,0:18:10.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茂木同學好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.52,0:18:12.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種人哪裏好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.66,0:18:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關燈了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.94,0:18:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.49,0:19:03.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡不著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.74,0:19:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  有點興奮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.64,0:19:10.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.22,0:19:16.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,積雪了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.56,0:19:17.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.19,0:19:20.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白色聖誕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.79,0:19:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 小晶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.15,0:19:32.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好懷念啊  以前經常來的啊 這個公園
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.47,0:19:35.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真虧富美醬你還記得
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.16,0:19:37.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.70,0:19:42.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了對了  搬家前一天富美醬在這裏哭了一天
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.76,0:19:44.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時真是辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.32,0:19:46.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有這事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.77,0:19:50.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有啊  不管我如何摸頭就是停不下來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.95,0:19:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不記得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.84,0:19:55.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 別裝傻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.21,0:19:56.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有在裝傻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.93,0:19:58.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富美醬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.03,0:20:05.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小學的校舍要沒了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.80,0:20:06.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.49,0:20:12.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得回到鎌倉了 一次都沒有去過
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.53,0:20:15.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該好好去看一下就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.16,0:20:16.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.20,0:20:17.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.87,0:20:20.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.11,0:20:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.23,0:20:26.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘了晚上的學校是很恐怖的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.37,0:20:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實有點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.84,0:20:38.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 富美醬 是不是該…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.22,0:20:41.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再去那邊看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.05,0:20:44.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  不要  等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.02,0:20:47.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不追上來就丟下你了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.71,0:20:51.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啦  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.78,0:21:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 下次再捉弄我的話 可不會輕易原諒你的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.35,0:21:19.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  為什麼一直忘記了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.03,0:21:25.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最早喜歡上的  我的初戀之人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.43,0:21:29.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到了嗎？明白了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.89,0:21:37.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  富美醬 我沒有在生氣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.17,0:21:40.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.58,0:21:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起來了  非常珍貴的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.28,0:21:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不覺就…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.72,0:21:55.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 那太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.73,0:21:57.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.46,0:22:04.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  那回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.12,0:22:06.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.32,0:22:21.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富美醬老是動不動就哭
